item.title: Airbnb Investment Project
item.description: Performed an analysis on the different neighborhoods around the Washington D.C. Area, specifically focusing on their investment potentials. These were ranked by datapoints such as their revenue, reviews, and customer preferences. From beginning to end, these data were cleaned by removing uncessary records, standardizing entried, and applying mathematical calculations. Presentation Data
